Title: High-Performance Off-Roaders
Plot: Jeremy puts the Renault Sport Twingo 133 through a stringent examination in Belfast with a helping hand from actor Ross Kemp. Richard samples the delights of airport vehicle racing, Guy Ritchie is the Star in a Reasonably Priced Car, and there is also a group test of the latest high-performance off-roaders from BMW, Audi and Range Rover.
ParentalRatingReason: Lightbox Provisional Classification. Official NZ Rating To Be Confirmed.
